# Composables

## Organization
- Composables are located in [src/common/composables/](mdc:src/common/composables).
- Each file provides reusable logic for a specific feature or concern (e.g., [useAuth.ts](mdc:src/common/composables/useAuth.ts), [useWebsocketInterface.ts](mdc:src/common/composables/useWebsocketInterface.ts)).

## Conventions
- Use the `useX` naming convention for composables.
- Export functions or reactive state for use in components.

## Example
- [useAuth.ts](mdc:src/common/composables/useAuth.ts): Authentication logic.
- [useWebsocketInterface.ts](mdc:src/common/composables/useWebsocketInterface.ts): WebSocket interface logic.
- [usePrompt.ts](mdc:src/common/composables/usePrompt.ts): Prompt dialog logic.
